{"lemma":"لَذّاتٌ","slug":"لَذّاتٌ","root":"ل.ذ.ذ","root_slug":"ل-ذ-ذ","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ذ-ذ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"لَذَّة","root":"لذذ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37683"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%B0%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of لَذَّ (laḏḏa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deliciousness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pleasure"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/lað.ða/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37683","headword_ar":"لَذَّةٌ","root":"l*","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pleasure; delight; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^alamN","text_ar":"اَلَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, L, K;) so explained because it happens not save to one who is of sound constitution, free from pains;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahowapN","text_ar":"شَهْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in one of the senses of this latter word], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearly so:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasantness; delightfulness; deliciousness; lusciousness, sweetness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the Lexicons passim: see the intrans. v."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*~a","text_ar":"لَذَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which it is an inf. n.) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*~aAtN","text_ar":"لَذَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, L, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*owaY","text_ar":"لَذْوَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolaY","text_ar":"فَعْلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*~apN","text_ar":"لَذَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and is formed by the change of one of the two dháls into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [in the L"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":";] a change similar to that in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaD~aY","text_ar":"تَقَضَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) It occurs in a trad. of 'Áïsheh, relating to the present world,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qado maDaY la*owaAhaA wabaqiYa balowaAhaA","text_ar":"قَدْ مَضَى لَذْوَاهَا وَبَقِىَ بَلْوَاهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its pleasure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasantness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delightfulness, hath passed away, and its probation remaineth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*~apN","text_ar":"لَذَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*aA*apN","text_ar":"لَذَاذَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*iy*N","text_ar":"لَذِيذٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*owaY","text_ar":"لَذْوَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eating and drinking in a state of ease, comfort,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasure, and competence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, L.) ―         -b4-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*iy*N","text_ar":"لَذِيذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}